   <div class='description_text'>
    
    The artist was part of Seattle Department of Transportation's Lake City Way Multi-Modal
    Improvements design team. He chose the site, worked with the design team to lay out paving and planting areas,
    and created construction drawings to incorporate into SDOT documents. The artist partnered with community leaders and
    residents to identify the best-loved aspects of the community and to evolve their expression. 

   <br />
    <br />  
